text: Alok Nembang (1973 - 6 November 2014) was a Nepali movie director. He was also a well-known music video director in Nepal for several decades. He was known for his movie Kohi Mero (2010). On November 6, 2014, Alok was found dead at his home in Kathmandu in an apparent suicide. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Suicides Category:Nepalese movie directors
